OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FFamilies and politicians are calling
OL,7,Ffor the former Chief Constable of
OL,8,FMerseyside Police to have his
OL,9,Fknighthood stripped.
OL,11,FIt comes after a damning IOPC report
OL,12,Fwhich said that Sir Norman Bettison
OL,13,Fwas one of a dozen officers who should
OL,14,Fhave faced gross misconduct charges
OL,15,Fover the Hillsborough disaster.
OL,17,FThe former police chief retired in
OL,18,F2013; the year after a criminal
OL,19,Finvestigation into actions taken by
OL,20,Fpolice during and after the
OL,21,FHillsborough disaster launched.
