OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) report has said if he
OL,8,Fwere still serving he would face
OL,9,Fproceedings for gross misconduct.
OL,11,FHe would be accused of being
OL,12,Fdeliberately dishonest about his
OL,13,Finvolvement in the 1989 disaster when
OL,14,Fhe applied to be Chief Constable of
OL,15,FMerseyside in 1998. Criminal charges
OL,16,Fagainst him were dropped in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
