OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FThe report, which said a total of 12
OL,7,Fofficers should have face misconduct
OL,8,Fhearings, said there would have been
OL,9,Fallegations that he downplayed his
OL,10,Frole in the aftermath of the disaster
OL,11,Fwhich killed 97 fans at the FA Cup
OL,12,Fsemi-final in 1989.
OL,14,FBettison was a chief inspector in
OL,15,FYorkshire at the time of the disaster.
OL,17,FIn 1998, he left West Yorkshire Police
OL,18,Fand became the chief constable of
OL,19,FMerseyside, despite facing bitter
OL,20,Fopposition from a number of the
OL,21,Fvictim's families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
