OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FMargaret Aspinall, who lost her 18-
OL,7,Fyear-old son James, is now questioning
OL,8,Fwhy Norman Bettison should keep his
OL,9,Fknighthood.
OL,11,FIan Byrne the Labour MP for West
OL,12,FDerby, who was at Hillsborough as the
OL,13,Fterrible events unfolded, wants the
OL,14,Fformer senior officer to lose his
OL,15,Fknighthood given to him in 2006 and
OL,16,FThe Queen's Police medal he was
OL,17,Fawarded.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
