OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FHe has written to the cabinet office
OL,7,Fminister Nick Thomas Symonds saying:
OL,8,F"I urge you in the strongest possible
OL,9,Fterms to make considered
OL,10,Frepresentation to the Prime Minister
OL,11,Fthat he immediately recommends to the
OL,12,FSovereign that Norman Bettison's
OL,13,FKnighthood be forfeited, for the
OL,14,Freason he is unworthy to retain it and
OL,15,Fin order to preserve the integrity of
OL,16,Fthe honours system".
OL,18,FByrne said his letter was in light of
OL,19,Fthe "utterly damning and frankly
OL,20,Fhideous findings of the IOPC" .
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
