OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FThe Liverpool City Region mayor Steve
OL,7,FRotheram, meanwhile, says the only
OL,8,Fjustice the 97 fans and their
OL,9,Frelatives will get now is that a new
OL,10,FHillsborough law is passed.
OL,12,FRotheram said justice remained
OL,13,F"agonisingly out of reach".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
