OL,3,CCalls for knighthood to be stripped
OL,4,Cfrom ex-police chief over Hillsborough
OL,6,FThe Public Office (Accountability)
OL,7,FBill would prevent public officials
OL,8,Ffrom telling lies to hearings like
OL,9,Finquiries and inquests, a duty of
OL,10,Fcandour. It is making it's way through
OL,11,Fparliament, but there have been fears
OL,12,Fby campaigners that it might be
OL,13,Fwatered down.
OL,15,F"The legacy of the 97 must now be
OL,16,Fjustice in law," he said.
